INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (32,2,'2012-08-03 14:56:17','2012-08-03 18:56:17','<strong>Compelled.</strong>\r\n\r\nAs a person, I have always been compelled to create, innovate and improve. It’s my way of puzzling out the workings of my world.\r\n\r\nAs the world is rich and varied, so is my media. My love of painting is sometimes trumped by the desire to go out and capture the world through my camera, or bring an object to life with my hands. This is why you will find paintings, photographs and handmade objects shown here.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','About Me','','publish','closed','closed','','about-me','','','2012-08-03 15:02:42','2012-08-03 19:02:42','',0,'http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/?post_type=banners&#038;p=32',0,'banners','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (35,2,'2012-08-03 14:55:54','2012-08-03 18:55:54','<strong>Compelled.</strong>\r\n\r\nAs a person, I have always been compelled to create, innovate and improve. It’s my way of puzzling out the workings of my world.\r\n\r\nAs the world is rich and varied, so is my media. My love of painting is sometimes trumped by the desire to go out and capture the world through my camera, or bring an object to life with my hands. This is why you will find paintings, photographs and handmade objects shown here.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','My Work','','publish','closed','closed','','my-work','','','2012-08-03 15:02:06','2012-08-03 19:02:06','',0,'http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/?post_type=banners&#038;p=35',0,'banners','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (37,2,'2012-08-07 11:22:27','2012-08-07 15:22:27','<h2><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/?attachment_id=185\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-185\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-185\" title=\"web-graphic-ECW\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/web-graphic-ECW.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"183\" /></a></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>\r\n<em></em></em>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #85592d;\"><strong><em><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/?attachment_id=109\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-109\"><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-109 alignnone\" title=\"PageLines- purses81220120801_0110.jpg\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/purses81220120801_0110-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>The Algonquin</em></strong></span></h3>\r\nThis relaxed yet sophisticated handbag offers style and everyday functionality. Shown in cream and black leather. The size of this bag is perfect carry on a quick outing or move it from briefcase to tote and keep all your essentials in one place.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #85592d;\"><strong><em><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/?attachment_id=170\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-170\"><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-170 alignnone\" title=\"sewing-material-brown-bag-2\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/sewing-material-brown-bag-2-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>The Sequoia</em></strong></span></h3>\r\nThis buttery deerskin bucket bag is stylish and just the right size to hold all the essentials. Shown in brown and natural deerskin. You’ve got to feel it to understand how soft it is! You are sure to get many comments when you carry this bag.\r\n<h3 align=\"left\"></h3>\r\n<h3 align=\"left\"></h3>\r\n<h3 align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #85592d;\"><strong><em><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/?attachment_id=174\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-174\"><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-174 alignnone\" title=\"sewing-material-2-bags\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/sewing-material-2-bags-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>The Tahoe</em></strong></span></h3>\r\n<p align=\"left\">This casual and carefree bag is handy for any outing. Shown in denim and brocade, this bag is nature-friendly, since no animal products are used in its production.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #85592d;\"><em><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/?attachment_id=172\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-172\"><img class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-172 alignnone\" title=\"SONY DSC\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/sewing-purse-materials-for-web-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a><strong>The Niagara</strong></em></span></h3>\r\n<p align=\"left\">This bag is perfect for a busy bride. It can hold lip gloss, small sprays, phone, money, feminine items and a handkerchief—all the things a bride needs on her big day. Shown in faux silk moiré fabric, adorned with beaded fringe and satin flowers. This is a perfect bridal shower gift.</p>\r\nThese bags also make excellent gifts for your bridesmaids and wedding party. Ask us about special requests to match bridal gowns.\r\n\r\nAll bags are carefully handcrafted and fully lined. They measure approximately 8 inches high and 5-1/2 inches across and weigh only a few ounces. Purse feet and a reinforced bottom allow bag to stand upright. Drawstring closure doubles as a wrist strap.','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home-2','','','2012-11-16 18:53:44','2012-11-16 22:53:44','',0,'http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/?page_id=37',1,'page','',0);
